title: Match History
body: When I try to look at my match history through the website it is just blank no matter what browser I try, and I also tried to clear my cookies/cache while also logging out of my account and logging back in.

replies.body:
First be sure that you're trying to log into the right region. It looks like you're playing on NA, so you would need to use [**this one**](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com).

If that doesn't help, and you've already cleared your cookies and web history, reach out to us in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so that we can look a little deeper.
